  "text": "Interestingly, Wld S provides significant suppression in mouse models of progressive motor neuron disease and glaucoma [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] , and moderate protection from chemotherapy-induced axon degeneration [CITATION_5] . These observations argue that defining the molecular mechanisms of axon degeneration in the context of WD could have an important therapeutic impact on the treatment of neurological disorders.",
